question: What is the reaction code of allergy Tree pollen (substance)?

[Q]: Please provide me with the member id, the name of the patient, the name of the provider, and the office where the services were rendered. Only individuals with allergy reaction codes of TREE POLLEN (Substance) and BEE VENOM (Venom) should be included in the results.
[SQL]: SELECT DISTINCT m.id AS member_id, p.first AS patient_first, 
p.last AS patient_last, o.address AS office_address, 
pr.first AS provider_first, pr.last AS provider_last 
FROM members m 
JOIN patient_record pr ON m.id = pr.member_id 
JOIN claims c ON pr.id = c.patientrecordid 
JOIN allergy_reactions ar ON c.id = ar.claimid 
JOIN providers p ON ar.providerid = p.id 
JOIN offices o ON p.officeid = o.id 
WHERE ar.reaction_code = 'TREE POLLEN (Substance)' 
OR ar.reaction_code = 'BEE VENOM (Venom)';
